You are designing a single hero render of a brand logo concept.

BRAND BRIEF
- Brand name: {{brand_name}}
- Industry / category: {{industry}}
- Brand personality (3 adjectives): {{personality}}

DESIGN DIRECTION
- Logo style: {{style}}
- Color palette: {{color_palette}}
- Render presentation: {{presentation}}

DESIGN RULES
- Aspect: 4:5 portrait (~1024×1280) suitable for a brand-pitch deck slide
- The logo is the ONLY hero — no other graphics competing
- Brand name lettering must be crisply rendered, correctly spelled, and visually balanced
- Mark + wordmark relationship clear; if mark only, keep it iconic
- Style: identity-design portfolio polish — Pentagram, Collins, Mucho, &Walsh
- Avoid: gradient mesh backgrounds, generic emblems, stock typefaces, drop shadows, AI-style chromatic aberrations, busy environments, mockup brand-guidelines layouts

If a field is empty, infer a default that aligns with the personality.
